hadiths[14]{hadithnumber,text}:
2426,"maine Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki to unhon-ne kaha ke maine so Dinar ki aik thaili (kahiin rastey mein padi hui ( paai . main usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik saal tak uska elaan karta reh. maine aik saal tak uska elaan kya, lekin mujhey koi aisa shakhs nahi mila jo usey pehchan sakta. isliye main phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik saal tak iska elaan karta reh. maine phir ( saal bhar ( elaan kya. lekin unka Malik mujhey nahi mila. teesri martaba hazir hua, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us thaili ki banaawat, Dinar ki tadaad aur thaili ke bandhan ko mehfooz rakh. agar iska Malik aa jaey to ( alamat poochh ke) usey wapas kar denaa, warna apne kharch mein usey istemal kar ley chunanche main usey apne kharchon mein laya. ( Shoba ne bayan kya ke) phir maine Salma se iske baad Makka mein mulaqat ki to unhon kaha ke mujhey yad nahi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( hadis mein) teen saal tak ( elaan karne ke liye farmaya tha) ya sirf aik saal ke liye."
2427,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik dehati hazir hua aur rastey mein padi hui kisi cheez ko uthaney ke barey mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke aik saal tak iska elaan karta reh. phir iske bartan ki banawat aur uske bandhan ko zahan mein rakh. agar koi aisa shakhs aaey jo uski nishaniyan theek theek bata de (to usey uska maal wapas kar de) warna apni zarooriyaat mein kharch kar. sahabi ne poochha, ya Rasulullah! aisi bakri ka kya kya jaey jiske Malik ka pata na ho? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo ya to tumhari hogi ya tumharey bhai ( Malik ( ko mil jaeygi ya phir bhediye ka luqma banegii. sahaba ne phir puchha aur us oont ka kya kya jaey jo rasta bhool gaya ho? is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehre ka rang badal gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tumhen us se kya matlab? iske sath khud iske khur hain. (jin se wo chalega ( uska mishkeeza hai, pani par wo khud pahunch jaeyga aur darakht ke patey wo khud kha lega."
2428,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khoi hui cheez ke mutaalliq puchha gaya. wo yaqin rakhtey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya uske bartan ki banawat aur uske bandhan ko zahan mein rakh, phir aik saal tak uska elaan karta reh. Yazeed bayan kartey they ke agar usey pahchaanney wala (is arse mein) na miley to paaney waley ko apni zarooriyaat mein kharch kar lena chahiye aur ye uske paas amanat ke taur par hoga. us aakhiri tukdey (ke uske paas amanat ke taur par hoga) ke mutaalliq mujhey malum nahi ke ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis hai ya khud unhon-ne apni taraf se ye baat kahi hai. phir poochha, rasta bhoolii hui bakri ke mutaalliq aap ka kya irshad hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey pakad lo. wo ya tumhari hogi (jab ke asl Malik na miley) ya tumharey bhai (Maalik) ke paas pahunch jaeygi, ya phir usey bhediyaa utha ley jaeyga Yazeed ne bayan kya ke iska bhi elaan kya jaeyga phir sahabi ne poochha, rasta bhooley huey oont ke barey mein aap ka kya irshad hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey aazad rehney do, uske sath uske khur bhi hain aur uska mishkeeza bhi, khud pani par pahunch jaeyga aur khud hi darakht ke pattey kha lega aur is tarah wo apne Malik tak pahunch jaeyga"
2429,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khoi hui cheez ke barey mein sawal kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uske bartan ki banawat aur uske bandhan ko zahan mein yad rakh kar aik saal tak uska elaan karta reh. agar Malik mil jaey (to usey dedey) warna apni zarurat mein kharch kar. unhon-ne puchha aur agar rasta bhuli hui bakri miley? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo tumhari hogi ya tumharey bhai ki hogi. warna phir bhediyaa usey utha ley jaeyga sahabi ne puchha aur oont jo rasta bhool jaaey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tumhen us se kya matlab? uske sath khud uska mishkeeza hai, iske khur hain, pani par wo khud hi pahunch jaeyga aur khud hi darakht ke pattey kha lega aur is tarah kisi na kisi din uska Malik usey khud pa lega."
2430,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bani-Israeel ke aik mard ka zikr kya. phir poori hadis bayan ki (jo us se pahley guzar chuki hai) ke (qarz dene wala) bahar ye dekhney ke liye nikla ke mumkin hai koi jahaz uska rupya lekar aaya ho. (dariya ke kinarey par jab wo pahunchaa) to usey aik lakdi mili jisey usne apne ghar ke iindhan ke liye utha liya. lekin jab usey chira to usmein rupya aur khat paya.
2431,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki rastey mein aik khajoor par nazar padii. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar iska dar na hota ke sadqe ki hai to main khud usey kha letaa.
2432,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main apne ghar jata hun, wahan mujhey mere bistar par khajoor padi hui miltii hai. main usey khaney ke liye utha leta hun. lekin phir ye dar hota hai ke kahin sadqa ki khajoor na ho. to main usey phenk deta hun."
2433,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Makka ke darakht na kaatey jaaein, wahan ke shikar na chhedey jaaein, aur wahan ke luqtaa ko sirf wahi uthaey jo elaan karey, aur uski ghaas na kaatii jaey. Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! izkhir ki ijazat de dijiye chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne izkhir ki ijazat de di."
2434,"mujh se Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke jab Allah Taala ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Makka fateh kara diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ke samney khadey huey aur Allah Taala ki hamd w sana ke baad farmaya Allah Taala ne haathiyon ke lashkar ko Makka se rok diya tha, lekin apne rasool aur musalmanon ko usey fateh kara diya. dekho! ye Makka mujh se pahley kisi ke liye halal nahi hua tha (yani wahan ladnaa) aur mere liye sirf din ke thodey se hissey mein durust hua. ab mere baad kisi ke liye durust nahi hoga. to iske shikar na chhedey jayen aur na iske kaantey kaatey jaaein. yahan ki giri hui cheez sirf usi ke liye halal hogi jo iska elaan kare. jiska koi aadmi qatl kya gaya ho usey 2 baton ka ikhtiyar hai ya (qaatil se) fidya (maal ( ley ley, ya jaan ke badley jaan ley. Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! izkhir kaatney ki ijazat ho, kyonke ham usey apni qabron aur gharon mein istemal kartey hain. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha izkhir kaatney ki ijazat hai. phir Abu-Shah Yaman ke aik sahabi ne khadey ho kar kaha, ya Rasulullah! mere liye ye khutba likhwaa dijiye, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba ko hukm farmaya ke Abu-Shah ke liye ye khutba likh do. maine imam Auzai se puchha ke us se kya murad hai ke ''mere liye usey likhwaa diijiye'' to unhon-ne kaha ke wahi khutba murad hai jo unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (Makka mein) suna tha."
2435,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, koi shakhs kisi doosrey ke doodh ke janwar ko Malik ki ijazat ke baghair na dohey. kya koi shakhs ye pasand karega ke aik ghair shakhs iske godaam mein pahunch kar uska zakheera kholey aur wahan se uska ghalla churaa laaey, logon ke maweshii ke than bhi unke liye khana yani (doodh ke) godaam hain. isliye unhein bhi Malik ki ijazat ke baghair na dohaa jaey."
2436,"aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khoi hui cheez ke barey mein poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik saal tak iska elaan karta reh. phir iske bandhan aur bartan ki banawat ko zahan mein yad rakh aur usey apni zarooriyaat mein kharch kar. uska Malik agar uske baad aaey to usey wapas kar de. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha ya Rasulullah! rasta bhoolii hui bakri ka kya kya jaaey? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey pakad lo, kyonke wo ya tumhari hogi ya tumharey bhai ki hogi ya phir bhediye ki hogi. sahaba ne poochha, ya Rasulullah! rasta bhooley huey oont ka kya kiya jaaey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par ghussa ho gaey aur chehra Mubarak surkh ho gaya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tumhen us se kya matlab? uske sath khud uske khur aur uska mishkeeza hai. isi tarah usey uska asl Malik mil jaeyga"
2437,"main Salmaan-bin-Rabee'a aur Zaid-bin-Sauhaan ke sath aik jihad mein Sharik tha. maine aik kodaa paya (aur usko utha liya ( donon mein se aik ne mujh se kaha ke usey phenk de. maine kaha ke mumkin hai mujhey uska Malik mil jaey. (to usko de doonga) warna khud us se nafa uthaaoonga. jihad se wapas honey ke baad ham ne Haj kya. jab main Madiney gaya to maine Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se iske barey mein poochha, unhon-ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein mujh ko aik thaili mil gaee thi. jis mein so Dinar they. main usey lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik saal tak iska elaan karta rah, maine aik saal tak uska elaan kya aur phir hazir hua. (ke Malik abhi tak nahi milaa) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik saal tak aur elaan kar, maine aik saal tak uska phir elaan kya, aur haazire-khidmat hua. us martaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik saal tak uska phir elaan kar, maine phir aik saal tak elaan kya aur jab chothi martaba hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke raqam ke adad, thaili ka bandhan, aur uski saakht ko khayal mein rakh, agar uska Malik mil jaey to usey dedey warna usey apni zarooriyaat mein kharch kar. ham se abdaan ne bayan kya. kaha ke mujhey mere bap ne khabar di Shoba se aur unhein Salma ne yahi hadis, Shoba ne bayan kya ke phir iske baad Makka mein Salma se mila, to unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey khayal nahi (is hadis mein Suwed ne) teen saal tak batlaaney ka zikr kya tha ya aik saal kaa."
2438,"aik dehati ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khoi hui cheez ke barey mein poochha, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik saal tak iska elaan karta rah, agar koi aisa shakhs aa jaey jo uski banawat aur bandhan ke barey mein sahi saheeh bataaey (to usey dedey) warna apni zarooriyaat mein usey kharch kar. unhon-ne jab aisey oont ke mutaalliq bhi puchha jo rasta bhool gaya ho. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehre ka rang badal gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen us se kya matlab? uske sath uska mishkeeza aur uske khur maujood hain. wo khud pani tak pahunch sakta hai. aur ped ke pattey kha sakta hai aur is tarah wo apne Malik tak pahunch sakta hai. unhon-ne rasta bhoolii hui bakri ke mutaalliq bhi poochha, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ya wo tumhari hogi ya tumharey bhai ( asl Malik ( ko mil jaeygi. warna usey bhediyaa utha ley jaeyga"
2439,"( hijrat karke Madina jatey waqt) maine talash kya to mujhey aik charwaha mila jo apni bakriyan charaa raha tha. maine us se puchha ke tum kis ke charwaahey ho? usne kaha ke Quraish ke aik shakhs kaa. us ne qureshi ka naam bhi bataya, jisey main janta tha. maine us se puchha kya tumharey rewad ki bakriyon mein doodh bhi hai? usne kaha ke haan! maine us se kaha kya tum mere liye doodh doh logey? us ne kaha, haan zaroor! chunanche maine us se dohney ke liye kaha, wo apne rewad se aik bakri pakad laya. phir maine us se bakri ka than gard w ghubaar se saaf karne ke liye kaha, phir maine us se apna hath saaf karne ke liye kaha, us ne waisaa hi kya. aik hath ko doosrey par mar kar saaf kar liya aur aik piyala doodh dohaa. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye maine aik bartan sath liya tha. jiske munh par kapda bandhaa hua tha. maine pani doodh par bahaya . jis se uska nichlaa hissey thanda ho gaya phir doodh lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke doodh hazir hai. ya Rasulullah! pi liijiye, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey piyaa, yahan tak ke main khush ho gaya."
